---
import AboutHeroImage from "../assets/blog-placeholder-about.jpg";
import Layout from "../layouts/BlogPost.astro";
---

<Layout
	title="About Me"
	description="A little about who I am and what I work on."
	pubDate={new Date("June 06 2026")}
	heroImage={AboutHeroImage}
>
	<p>
		Hi, I'm <strong>Bowei</strong> — a software developer. I like taking rough
		ideas and turning them into things that actually work. This site is where I
		write about what I'm building and what I learn along the way.
	</p>

	<h3>What I do</h3>
	<p>
		Most of my time goes into writing code: building features, debugging, and
		reading more documentation than I'd like to admit. I care about software that
		feels fast, stays out of the way, and respects the people using it.
	</p>

	<h3>What I'm working on</h3>
	<p>
		Right now I'm building <strong>memex</strong>, a personal knowledge tool
		inspired by Vannevar Bush's 1945 idea of a machine that helps us think and
		remember. I write about its progress here on the blog.
	</p>

	<h3>What I care about</h3>
	<ul>
		<li>Small, focused tools over heavy all-in-one platforms</li>
		<li>Clear writing and good documentation</li>
		<li>Writing things down so I don't have to relearn them later</li>
	</ul>

	<h3>Get in touch</h3>
	<p>
		You can find me on <a href="https://github.com/Xu929-X1">GitHub</a> or reach
		me at <a href="mailto:boweixu929@gmail.com">boweixu929@gmail.com</a>.
	</p>
</Layout>
